  "description": "Herm\u00e8s Kelly 35 \u2013 Box Calf \u2013 Ebene Brown \u2013 1993 \nAn extraordinary vintage Herm\u00e8s Kelly 35 crafted in classic Box Calf leather in rich Ebene (dark chocolate) brown, dating to 1993. \nBox Calf from the 1990s is highly coveted for its structured silhouette, glossy finish, and the way it develops a refined patina over time. Finding a Kelly of this era in excellent condition, with clean corners, strong structure, and beautiful surface sheen, is increasingly rare. Many examples from this period show significant wear or loss of shape\u2014this one presents beautifully and has been exceptionally preserved.\nThe 35cm size offers elegant proportions\u2014large enough for everyday sophistication, yet timeless and ladylike in silhouette. The deep Ebene shade is one of Herm\u00e8s\u2019 most classic and versatile browns, pairing effortlessly with both neutrals and richer tones. Comes with removable strap,clochette, padlock, keys and dustbag.\n\nSKU006000",
